This library is a replacement (a complete rewrite and redesign) of an earlier localization solution posted on CodeProject in 2009 - Advanced WPF Localization (https://codeproject.com/Articles/249369/Advanced-WPF-Localization).

Documentation:
https://github.com/JechoJekov/WpfLocalization/wiki
https://github.com/JechoJekov/WpfLocalization/blob/master/README.md

Demo project:
https://github.com/JechoJekov/WpfLocalization/wiki/Demo-project
]]>
